chestnut &amp; the <unclear xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">emminence</unclear> where <unclear xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"/>
