            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">Pol</hi> Nature in this view is probably<lb/>
nearly the same as it was 2000 years<lb/>
ago; but <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
