            <lb/>
results may be submitted to calculation<lb/>
The fact of the combination of bodies<lb/>
in definite proportions has led to the revival<lb/>
of that ancient doctrine of the Greek<lb/>
School attributed to <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
