result. This doctrine which in its<lb/>
application to Chemistry has been called<lb/>
the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">atomic doctrine</hi>, or theory, has been<lb/>
embraced by several modern Chemists;<lb/>
but the development of it is owing to<lb/>
