                xml:id="ttag123"
                ref="#person_066"
                type="person">
               <name xml:id="tag123" type="person">
          M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Dalton
        </name>
            </rs>, who seems to have been the<lb/>
first person to generalize the facts of<lb/>
