to see equally well through a clear<lb/>
glass &amp; one covered with smoke;<lb/>
but there is still the one <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">sentient</hi>
            <lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">principle</hi>. To suppose that because<lb/>
